Hello QA,

This is a reminder that you will lose swedishcandy.eu on Tuesday 7th of March because you previously cancelled your renewal.

We urge you to keep in mind that if you don’t renew your subscription ASAP, you will no longer own your domain name. This means that competitors can buy it and you will no longer have the option to purchase it back.

97% of consumers use the web to search for local businesses; you will miss out on all of these customers without a domain name.

If you wish to renew your subscription reach out to customer service immediately. If you wish to lose almost all of your customers to competitors, no further action is required.

Kind Regards,

The FreeLogoServices Customer Service Team
